parameters:
[Olivia] I'm glad you came. I wanted to express my
gratitude.

[Masamune] I just did my best for my own purpose,
you know.

[Olivia] Even so, if you weren't here, the academy
would have been in a lot of trouble.

[Olivia] I think it's safe as long as I'm at the
academy regarding the contract with the demon.

[Olivia] It would be good to take it easy for a
while.

[Masamune] I'll be allowed to do so. I received a
message from my superior that it's still okay for
me to stay at the academy.

[Masamune] By the way, are you currently in your
human form?
[Olivia] Living flesh... Ah, about the doll magic.

[Olivia] That's right, since the doll was
destroyed. It's going to be tough going back to
school after such a long time.

[Masamune] So it really was a doll. To think
there's such an intricate creation... amazing
magic.

[Sayoko] Olivia is a genius, after all. She's on
the path to becoming the future president of the
Magic Association.
[Masamune] But, what is she always doing?

[Olivia] I study and practice magic in my room.
The classes are at a low level, so...

[Olivia] Maintaining dolls is quite difficult, you
know.

[Masamune] (I wonder if the reason she
occasionally disappears is because she's doing
maintenance...)

[Masamune] I see. So that means you're better at
planetary magic.

[Sayoko] By the way, we can also share
sensitivity.
[Sayoko] You can also have casual sex, you know.

[Sayoko] Could it be that in some loop, you were
having sex with Masamune all the time?

[Masamune] No, I haven't done it with him. But
there have been moments where we've gotten close,
like with Jackson.

[Olivia] Unbelievable... Maybe they just let me do
it with the dolls to satisfy me.

[Sayoko] What are you sighing about? Masamune has
Amelia, right?

[Masamune] I'm not relieved or anything. Besides,
Amelia is no longer my girlfriend.
[Sayoko] So that means you're single, huh?

[Masamune] That's right, but it doesn't really
matter.

[Sayoko] What about my Olivia? She's surprisingly
reserved, you know.

[Sayoko] But our roommate was talking about it.
They said you're always masturbating.
[Sayoko] And you're a spoiled brat too.

[Olivia] That person is a perverted exhibitionist,
so don't take it seriously.
[Sayoko] Ah, I forgot the main topic. Olivia.

[Olivia] I called you here to invite you to join
the student council.

[Olivia] If you're interested, why not join? In
fact, I'm thinking of nominating you as the next
vice president.

[Masamune] To that extent... Sayo... Even though
Hiyo is here.

[Sayoko] If you become the vice president, it
might be difficult for you to move around since
you're a spy, right?

[Olivia] That's why there are no candidates. The
talented people have been taken by the Magic
Research Club.
[Masamune] Indeed, there are only two of us here.

[Olivia] So? I think there's no problem with your
abilities, but...

[Masamune] I... don't know how long I can stay
here. Besides, there's also the matter of
Leviathan.

[Olivia] You don't have to worry about the
Leviathan matter while you're at the academy.

[Olivia] I don't feel anything special from you
right now.

[Olivia] If you're here, I'll feel relieved even
after graduation.
[Masamune] I'll think about it for now.

[Masamune] (Being in the student council... it's a
good way to gather information, but)
